## Step-by-Step Data Creation

### Step 1: Collection Types (Auto-created by V3 migration)

```sql
-- Already created by migration
SELECT * FROM collection_types;
```

**Result:**
```
+----+---------------+
| ID | NAME          |
+----+---------------+
|  1 | CATEGORY      |
|  2 | YOUTUBE_SET   |
|  3 | LEARNING_PATH |
+----+---------------+
```

