### Step 2: Create a Admin User

```sql
-- First, create an admin user to own questions
INSERT INTO users (ID, EMAIL, NAME, PASSWORD_HASH, ROLE, IS_ACTIVE)
VALUES (1, 'admin@example.com', 'Admin User', '$2a$10$...hashed...', 'ADMIN', 1);
```

