### Step 7: Link Questions to Collections

```sql
-- Add Question 1 (Closure) to JavaScript category
INSERT INTO question_collections (QUESTION_ID, COLLECTION_ID, ORDER_INDEX)
VALUES (1, 1, 1);

-- Add Question 2 (Async) to JavaScript category
INSERT INTO question_collections (QUESTION_ID, COLLECTION_ID, ORDER_INDEX)
VALUES (2, 1, 2);

-- Add Question 1 to YouTube set "Top 10 JS"
INSERT INTO question_collections (QUESTION_ID, COLLECTION_ID, ORDER_INDEX)
VALUES (1, 2, 1);

-- Add Question 2 to YouTube set "Top 10 JS"
INSERT INTO question_collections (QUESTION_ID, COLLECTION_ID, ORDER_INDEX)
VALUES (2, 2, 2);
```

**question_collections table:**
```
+-------------+---------------+-------------+
| QUESTION_ID | COLLECTION_ID | ORDER_INDEX |
+-------------+---------------+-------------+
|           1 |             1 |           1 |  ← Closure in JavaScript category
|           2 |             1 |           2 |  ← Async in JavaScript category
|           1 |             2 |           1 |  ← Closure in YouTube set
|           2 |             2 |           2 |  ← Async in YouTube set
+-------------+---------------+-------------+
```

**Visual:**
```
JavaScript Category (ID: 1)
  ├─ [1] Closure
  └─ [2] Async/Await

Top 10 JS Video (ID: 2)
  ├─ [1] Closure
  └─ [2] Async/Await
```

---

### Step 8: Tag Questions

```sql
-- Tag Question 1 (Closure) with "closure" and "scope"
INSERT INTO question_tags (QUESTION_ID, TAG_ID) VALUES
(1, 1),  -- closure tag
(1, 2);  -- scope tag

-- Tag Question 2 (Async) with "async", "promise", "event-loop"
INSERT INTO question_tags (QUESTION_ID, TAG_ID) VALUES
(2, 3),  -- async tag
(2, 4),  -- promise tag
(2, 5);  -- event-loop tag
```

**question_tags table:**
```
+-------------+--------+
| QUESTION_ID | TAG_ID |
+-------------+--------+
|           1 |      1 |  ← Closure has "closure" tag
|           1 |      2 |  ← Closure has "scope" tag
|           2 |      3 |  ← Async has "async" tag
|           2 |      4 |  ← Async has "promise" tag
|           2 |      5 |  ← Async has "event-loop" tag
+-------------+--------+
```

