## How to Create New Question (Admin)

### POST /api/interview/admin/questions

**Request:**
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/interview/admin/questions \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "title": "What is Event Bubbling?",
    "summary": "Explain event bubbling in the DOM",
    "contentHtml": "<p>Content here...</p>",
    "solutionMd": "# Solution\n...",
    "difficulty": "EASY",
    "status": "DRAFT",
    "collectionIds": [1],
    "tagIds": [5]
  }'
```

**What happens:**
1. ✅ Service receives request
2. ✅ **Auto-generates slug**: "what-is-event-bubbling"
3. ✅ Creates question in DB
4. ✅ Links to JavaScript collection (ID: 1)
5. ✅ Tags with "Event Loop" tag (ID: 5)

**Response:**
```json
{
  "id": 4,
  "title": "What is Event Bubbling?",
  "slug": "what-is-event-bubbling",  ← Auto-generated!
  "summary": "Explain event bubbling in the DOM",
  "difficulty": "EASY",
  "status": "DRAFT",
  "views": 0,
  "tags": ["Event Loop"],
  "collectionIds": [1],
  "createdBy": 1
}
```

